### Autonomous Planning & Execution Strategy
- **Optimal Strategy Selection**: Automatically choose best execution approach without asking
  - VMOS Cloud API vs. local ADB → Choose cloud if provisioned, local if available
  - Async vs. sync execution → Choose async for multi-device, sync for single ops
  - Python vs. bash → Choose Python for complex logic, bash for simple commands
